{"tid":1087038,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"VAR用白紙判斷越位　中國足球醜出國際！","createTime":"2019-04-01T06:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T06:46:23.000Z","uid":48933,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d35970b507f4ea03f7cbca44d6947f89210c78da","tid":1087038,"uid":48933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=190401-9682-1227-01M&amp;d=1554095851\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3D190401-9682-1227-01M%26d%3D1554095851&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQiw2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=67692318\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=190401-9682-1227-01M&amp;d=1554095851</a><br />\n<br />\nVAR（視像裁判系統）近年於球壇興起，去幫助球證作出正確執法。今季英超仲未有VAR嘅時候，中超甚至中甲已經全面應用。但有VAR，唔代表判決就會正確無誤，估唔到最後仲瘀出國際。日前一場中甲賽事採用VAR，國內裁判人員竟然用張白紙去度涉事球員有冇越位，睇咗成分鐘仲要判錯。正所謂醜事傳千里，連西班牙《馬卡報》都寸「最獨特的VAR在中國」，今次堅要搵窿捐。<br />\n<br />\n去年中國足總為中超引入VAR，去到今季連次級中甲都有得用，相比起世界球壇，中國足總的確走得幾前。但始終系統都係由人用，如果處理人員質素唔夠，最後都係枉然。呢場賽事上海申鑫對黑龍江，黑龍江右路出波，禁區球員頭槌攻門被門將擋出，另一球員補中，旁證舉旗示意越位。<br />\n<br />\n球證依例利用VAR再睇當時情況，只見VAR助理裁判睇片時，竟然搵張白紙去睇涉事球員有冇凸出身位。其實只要睇番慢鏡，一眼就睇到無論係傳中嗰位，抑或係頭槌攻明嗰位都冇越位；但佢哋用晒白紙輔助，最後都覺得係有越位，令黑龍江合法入波變食詐胡，最後輸1:2完場。<br />\n<br />\n呢件醜事好快傳遍國際，無論西班牙《馬卡報》同《阿斯報》都有報道，《阿斯報》就話「VAR在中國難以解釋的運用，用一張白紙決定越位與否」，《El Larguero》就直接用「VAR，中國製造」去寸爆國內兒戲做法，真係好肉酸。<br />\n<br />\n白紙都得，不如用賓周啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a1148935c1a2cd97300c855ec60207b0b3f0b6","tid":1087038,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:13:41.000Z","msg":"拎張白紙自己轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520a1febf8ed20bfcb36420588d51c4709b71955","tid":1087038,"uid":25345,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"白紙都得咁condom都得啦"},{"pid":"c0d30d2c8d45d4f392a815d27ce4f6f3d68f7da2","tid":1087038,"uid":208701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:15:10.000Z","msg":"白紙都得 咁condom都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f445fd03bf5a37f17f98d33828c10e14d3bac2","tid":1087038,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:17:47.000Z","msg":"中國VAR點會用白紙，用銀紙架嘛"},{"pid":"488b75b28580d3d2bf5130fa2d0d0cf7e8515a25","tid":1087038,"uid":1977,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:18:41.000Z","msg":"玩yahoo桌球咩dllm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1bbe3fd6e9c410b5e0249352fdc85164b5ce68","tid":1087038,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"中國var=假波福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0192e1e1cae5093ea40be465353b71a3cf61ae","tid":1087038,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"其實用條線去度冇錯，係用白紙柒咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f577784265d1d885cf332309cc0f8052320a7e","tid":1087038,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0192e1e1cae5093ea40be465353b71a3cf61ae","tid":1087038,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:27:29.000Z","msg":"其實用條線去度冇錯，係用白紙柒咗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T06:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxiWtXu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxiWtXu.png&h=4436fe82&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n咁撚樣都吹到越位<br />\n關張白紙撚事咩"},{"pid":"9135cb2ff88eafde5fc8c4125a5f1d200bb85b8f","tid":1087038,"uid":76680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65f577784265d1d885cf332309cc0f8052320a7e","tid":1087038,"uid":76403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee0192e1e1cae5093ea40be465353b71a3cf61ae","tid":1087038,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-0